{"tid":1324440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳示威者鉗斷警員手指『工具』實為警棍 警方誤放消息低調修改","createTime":"2019-07-16T14:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T16:01:52.000Z","uid":53379,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"22bae3d3fdfdbd12e7704ea4775b0f6a0b971bbf","tid":1324440,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:30:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>傳示威者鉗斷警員手指『工具』實為警棍 警方誤放消息低調修改</strong></span><br />\n【Fact Check剪鉗夾斷手指】沙田新城市廣場周日發生嚴重警民衝突，多間媒體引述警方消息指，有警員被示威者用鉗剪斷手指。但傳真社調查發現，被指剪斷警員手指的剪鉗，實為示威者從警員手上搶去的警棍。部分傳媒其後刪走相關內容，但警方從未正式澄清。傳真社向警方求證未獲正面回覆，只著記者翻查警方新聞稿及電台訪問內容。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/66668972_1168811376659248_5994127229552951296_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_oc=AQk7AZTsOiMERUrLWGr_B2VxR-eOUD3O88iqayKUJBE68hSd3M78JXeADw0dflqyJmA&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=f75f89337cc49b305942949cf1dbe122&amp;oe=5DA2F96A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F66668972_1168811376659248_5994127229552951296_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_oc%3DAQk7AZTsOiMERUrLWGr_B2VxR-eOUD3O88iqayKUJBE68hSd3M78JXeADw0dflqyJmA%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Df75f89337cc49b305942949cf1dbe122%26oe%3D5DA2F96A&h=6589f325&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/factwire/photos/a.437287353144991/1168811373325915/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffactwire%2Fphotos%2Fa.437287353144991%2F1168811373325915%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=4wcocBccBPvk8MIeFEbr%2BcdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=77bdc6fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/factwire/photos/a.437287353144991/1168811373325915/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"e3c202570326d6fe2cc346cbff916e4d9fb6a00b","tid":1324440,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji