class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992654995eb1ec19157fd3616a418b5323737f36","tid":1324440,"uid":152387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:01:52.000Z","msg":"每次見到呢啲片段都覺得好唏噓<br />\n當一大班示威者打落單警察嘅時候,時不時見到和理非拉開示威者保護警察<br />\n但當一大班公安圍毆示威者嘅時候,從來都唔見有警察主動保護示威者拉開公安"}]}